+ Components

= Modular tools to add functionality to an article.

* [[[component:earthworm|]]], a decorative multi-article navigation widget
* [[[component:tz|]]], a tool to convert a time and timezone to the reader's native timezone
* [[[component:theme-squares|]]], a componentised version of [[*user Woedenaz]]'s theme colour squares
* [[[component:pages|]]], a pagination generator that will display a wide range of formats
* [[[component:carousel|]]], exactly what it says on the tin
* [[[component:fade-in|]]], to make your article fade in slowly
* [[[component:croqstyle|]]], some misc CSS utilities for drafting and documenting

